ğŸ¥ Hospital Management System â€“ Doctor Portal

A desktop-based **Hospital Management System (Doctor Portal)** built using **Java (Swing)** and **MySQL**.
The system allows doctors to manage their **profiles**, view/edit **appointments**, and upload/manage **research papers** â€” all in one place.
Uses **Object-Oriented Programming (OOP)** concepts throughout the architecture.

---

## ğŸš€ Features

### **1. Doctor Profile Management**

* Dynamic profile loading via Doctor ID
* Displays profile picture, name, specialization, qualification etc
* Stores updated information in MySQL database


**2. Appointment Management**

* Built-in calendar view
* Doctors can add, edit, and delete appointments
* Shows patient details
* On-spot changes updated in real-time
* Efficient for daily scheduling

**3. Research Paper Management**

* Upload research papers
* View list of submitted papers
* Delete papers if needed
*Log for Doctors research papers

